erate an alert email. This will only work if both Subtract Stock &amp; Track Inventory are set as \'Yes\'.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Condition identifier</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p> User defined field to define a particular product\'s condition in the system. Possible inputs for this field are \'New\', \'Used\' &amp; \'Refurbished\'.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Digital Product Max Download time</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field to define maximum number of times a digital product can be downloaded. Possible inputs for this field are integers.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Download validity in days</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field to define maximum number of days until the digital product can be downloaded. Possible inputs for this field are integers.</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Title</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field to define the title of the product in the shop. </p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Comments</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p> User defined field to input comments for the product.</p>                                        </li>                                                                                  \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>URL Keyword</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field for input of URL keywords, used for URL rewriting.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Added on </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined date field to input the date the product is added into the system. Date format is mm/dd/yy</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Available from </h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p> User defined date field to input the date the product is available from. Date format is mm/dd/yy</p>                                        </li>                                         \r\n				<li>                                                                                      \r\n					<h5>Active</h5>                                                                                      \r\n					<p>User defined field to mark a particular product as Active in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are \'Yes\' &amp; \'No\'. Default value sho