(48, 1, 'Men\'s T-Shirt', '', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: SourceSansPro; vertical-align: baseline; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Splatter your casual wardrobe with a splash of style with clothing from DNMX. This trendy brand offers absolute fashion along with unbeatable comfort for the style happy.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: transparent; font-family: SourceSansPro; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin: 0px; font-size: inherit; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">DNMX Clothing for Men</h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit; font-family: SourceSansPro; vertical-align: baseline; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Start your search with&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: transparent; font: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; border-radius: 0px;\">DNMX T-shirts</span>. The collection carries everything from tropical printed slim fit tees to hooded burnout T-shirts. Next up, are DNMX shirts for men. For a trendy look, get a look at their checked hooded shirts with kangaroo pockets and tropical printed shirts.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ajio.com/dnmx-slub-knit-crew-neck-t-shirt/p/440750731_offwhite?gclid=EAIaIQobChMIxrbj4uqd5QIVjRiPCh386gN9EAQYAyABEgKGAPD_BwE#\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outli